						               													<description>Expansion for the game In the Palm of your Hand: try to make your teammate guess the right card by miming it using the objects in the box in the palm of their hand as their eyes remain closed.&amp;#10;Discover beautiful illustrations showing the life of Mei, wife of the first hero of the game, Leon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this expansion, discover &amp;laquo;The Life of Mei&amp;raquo; from her childhood to the encounter with Leon. See the story of the core game through the eyes of this new character! Adds a nice replay value to the core game with 50 new cards and 2 new objects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mix the 50 cards of this expansion with the 100 cards of the core game. Add the 2 new objects to the ones from the core game. Play as usual and discover the life of the characters from another angle. Find new ways to mime the cards of the base game thanks to the new objects, as well as new ways to use the objects of the base game thanks to the 50 new cards. The cards also bring new possibilities to interfere with the memories!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
